snippet.title: SEDAP! -- Forest Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist SEDAP! on Steam!

SEDAP! is a 2-player co-op game where players collaborate to cook scrumptious Southeast Asian dishes while exploring the mysterious Khaya Island. The game celebrates the rich diversity of cuisines and cultures found in Southeast Asia. The exclamation “sedap!” means “delicious!” in the Malay language.

The game is currently under development by Singaporean indie dev team kopiforge (Jay Wong, Nadiyah Toi and Foo Jing Ting), with original music composed by Rebecca Tan Ting Yan. 

SEDAP! is slated for a full release in early 2025 for PC and eventually, consoles.
